		<h1>Release Notes</h1>
		<div class="descr">Updated for Snowmix 0.5.1.1</div>

		<p>This is the Release Notes for Snowmix.</p>

		<ul>
			<li>Release Notes for version <a href="#0.5.1.1">0.5.1.1</a>.</li>
			<li>Release Notes for version <a href="#0.5.1">0.5.1</a>.</li>
			<li>Release Notes for version <a href="#0.5.0">0.5.0</a>.</li>
		</ul>

		<p>If you are looking for the Release Notes for versions prior to version 0.5.0, please see
