	<div class="item">
		<h1><a name="0.5.1.1">Snowmix version 0.5.1.1</a></h1>
		<div class="descr">Released July 2020</div>

		<h3>Overall Theme</h3>
		<br/>

		<p>The overall theme of this release is to update bootstrap scripts and input/output scripts
		to ease compiling, installing and running Snowmix on a long list of OS distributions
		that has been released since Snowmix 0.5.1 was originally released.</p>

		<p>Please the <a href="[HOME]Intro/compileandinstall.html#comments">platform comments</a> for a list of distros tested with this release.</p>

		<p><strong>Compile and install:</strong><br/>
		Please see the
		<a href="[HOME]Intro/compileandinstall.html">compile and install instructions</a>.
		for version 0.5.1.1.</p>


